{"tid":907862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"包皮：「卡尼」冇不和","createTime":"2018-11-19T07:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T07:55:39.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c324533b54654a4038a6a2a6e2dfeb33b096a2b","tid":907862,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=1qQUYiz6aatzlv%2BlB%2BK4%2FjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b4beb253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】尼馬及卡雲尼在日前友賽再爆不和消息，巴黎聖日耳門隊友基利安麥巴比強調兩人沒有心病。<br />\n<br />\n上季於巴黎聖日耳門，尼馬及卡雲尼已經爆出爭射12碼的決裂事件，到上周五友賽，巴西以1:0小勝烏拉圭，卡雲尼更於85分鐘兇狠攔截射入12碼的尼馬，令兩人不和的傳聞再次升溫。<br />\n<br />\n基利安麥巴比（Kylian Mbappe）作為他們於PSG的前線拍檔，強調兩人沒有心病：「卡雲尼是一名出色的球員，對PSG也很好。發生在尼馬身上的事，我在WhatsApp向他傳了短片，他一笑置之，所以根本沒有不和。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是一次爭球，他們各自為國效命，應該這樣做，兩人都付出所有。之後回到PSG不會有後續，他們將會擁抱對方，齊齊入球，沒有問題。」麥巴比續說。"},{"pid":"050fe7c5c9ab72b23389e75fc0c754c1bb27696d","tid":907862,"uid":27274,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"仆街會唔會係要麥巴比出黎解話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadfc2c7005a11c5ed74e440753e2051cbc0bc09","tid":907862,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"以為哈利卡尼"},{"pid":"89318fb47f23edfc671ceb131d9834d78e2b03f3","tid":907862,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"愈解釋愈似有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bccf35c98ca5f965d6030681d9e553149e5171f","tid":907862,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"大佬話冇心病就算有都變冇"},{"pid":"b63585950899a7ee1ffba7f758c96e55a842f998","tid":907862,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"龜頭"},{"pid":"73dbb4af907caeea8212ed1a208629dfaa301a2b","tid":907862,"uid":187